================================================================================
I3DShapesTool (Python port)
================================================================================

The .i3d.shapes binary decoder in this add-on (modules i3d_shapes_reader,
i3d_shapes_models, i3d_shapes_to_meshdata, _cipher_keys) is a Python port
of the C# decoder logic from the I3DShapesTool project. Earlier releases
of this add-on bundled a Windows .exe built from a fork of the same
project; that .exe has been removed in favor of the pure-Python
implementation, but the attribution remains because the decoding logic
is still substantially derived from the original work.

Original project:
    I3DShapesTool
    Author:  Daniel Hultgren (Donkie)
    Source:  https://github.com/Donkie/I3DShapesTool

